@startuml MCP Aggregators
!theme plain

actor "AI Agent" as agent

rectangle "MCP Proxy" as aggregator

rectangle "MCP Server A\n(10 tools)" as a
rectangle "MCP Server B\n(15 tools)" as b
rectangle "MCP Server C\n(12 tools)" as c

agent -> aggregator : query
aggregator ..> a : load on demand
aggregator ..> b
aggregator ..> c

note bottom
  **Problem:** 50 tools overwhelm agent context
  **Solution:** Dynamic loading, only relevant tools
end note

@enduml
